### Register a new Teacher User and Teacher Record with Multiple Institutions
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher.alice.jones@example.com",
  "password": "teacherPassword456&",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Jones",
  "subjectExpertise": "Mathematics, Physics",
  "bio": "Experienced math and physics teacher.",
  "profilePictureUrl": "http://example.com/profiles/alice.jpg",
  "institutionIds": [1, 2],
  "primaryInstitutionId": 1
}

### Register another teacher (minimal data with single institution)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher.bob.williams@example.com",
  "password": "bobTeacherPass789*",
  "firstName": "Bob",
  "lastName": "Williams",
  "institutionIds": [3]
}

